rate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/39851/', '', 'Suvorexant, Triazolam, Flurazepam, Methohexital, Pentobarbital, Dichloralphenazone, Valerian, Butabarbital, Secobarbital, Chloral hydrate, Quazepam, More', 'Artesunate, Lumefantrine, Pyrimethamine, Tafenoquine, Atovaquone, Halofantrine, Primaquine, Proguanil, Sulfadoxine', 1767369485);
